Background
 The Department of War Education Activity (DoWEA) is seeking to enhance its capabilities through comprehensive contractor services for data modernization, artificial intelligence (AI) integration, and enterprise analytics. 
This initiative is aimed at supporting the Chief Data and Artificial Intelligence Office (CDAO) in achieving its mission.

Work Details
 The contractor will provide services across seven core functional areas: 
1. Data Architecture and Engineering; 
2. Analytics and Business Intelligence; 
3. Data Governance; 
4. AI Integration; 
5. Data and AI Literacy; 
